    M -->|Save listing| N[Saved / Shortlist Page<br/>Wireframe: saved.png]
    M -->|Contact owner| O[Contact Owner Section<br/>Inside detail-view.png]

    N --> P([End])
    O --> P

    R --> R1[Browse Roommate Posts]
    R1 --> R2[View Roommate Post Details]
    R2 --> R3[Contact or Save Roommate Post]
    R3 --> P

    S --> S1{Select role}
    S1 -->|Student| C
    S1 -->|Apartment Owner| OW[Owner Add Listing Form<br/>Wireframe: input-form.png]
    S1 -->|Admin| AD[Admin Dashboard<br/>Wireframe: dashboard.png]

    OW --> OW1[Submit Apartment Listing]
    OW1 --> OW2[Show validation or success message]
